@startuml signupSequenceDiagram_2

actor Admin
actor "New User" as NewUser
participant "React Frontend" as FE
participant "Ory Oathkeeper" as Oathkeeper
participant "Spring Boot Backend" as BE
participant "Ory Kratos\n(Admin API)" as KratosAdmin
participant "Ory Kratos\n(Public API)" as KratosPublic
participant "Ory Keto" as Keto
participant "Kratos Courier" as Courier
participant "SMTP / Mailpit" as SMTP

== New User: Account Activation ==

NewUser -> SMTP : Open email client\n(or Mailpit UI)
SMTP --> NewUser : Recovery code email\n{ code: recoveryCode }

NewUser -> FE : Navigate to /registration\nand fill activation form\n(email, code, password, confirmPassword)

note over FE : Frontend validates\npassword === confirmPassword\nbefore submitting

FE -> Oathkeeper : POST api.irboard.local/v1/auth/activate\n+ { email, code, password }\n[rule: api-backend-activate-public\nauthenticator: noop → allow]
Oathkeeper -> BE : POST /v1/auth/activate\n+ { email, code, password }\n(no X-User — public endpoint)

BE -> BE : userRepository.findByEmail(email)\n→ retrieve pendingActivationToken (flowId)

BE -> KratosPublic : POST /self-service/recovery?flow={flowId}\n{ method: code, code: recoveryCode }

alt Valid code
    KratosPublic --> BE : 422 Unprocessable Entity\n(expected — flow advanced to\nsettings phase, code accepted)

    BE -> KratosAdmin : PUT /admin/identities/{oryId}\n+ Bearer {apiKey}\n{ schema_id: default, state: active,\n  traits: { ... },\n  credentials: { password: { config:\n    { password: password } } } }
    KratosAdmin --> BE : 200 OK\n(password set on identity)

    BE -> BE : user.setActive(true)\nuser.setPendingActivationToken(null)\nuserRepository.save(user)
    BE --> Oathkeeper : 200 OK { userId, email, ... }
    Oathkeeper --> FE : 200 OK { userId, email, ... }

    ==  ==
end
@enduml